{
  "stem": "25288.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was there in a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was working in a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A couple years later, we heard he passed away over there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He died over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And then we find out he survive with a young child-- lives in Budapest-- and very hard condition.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So some people who were in this group, and lived in Budapest, they organized, in every month-- or week, or two weeks-- somebody sended for the-- for this woman, a care package.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I send that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My turn was maybe two or three times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And every time when I send her the package, I had a nice thank you note from this woman.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, the last-- and we send them a picture of her husband, of commanding officer.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The last package, when I sent her, she sended thank you note.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she asked me not to send anymore, because he got a nice job, and he can support himself and his son.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And several years ago, when the Yad Vashem was organized, that was in the '90s-- and I remember that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I thought, this man would deserve to remember him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I wrote that down, the whole story of what happened, and how it happened, and how-- how she saved our live, those 150, 160 people, how he served.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in English, I am not so perfect.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So mine daughter helped me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She translated in English.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I send it into the Yad Vashem-- took it to Jerusalem.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And other two friends, who was-- we were together in the camp-- I had a paper to sign.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This-- this story is true.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were-- we were together in this camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
